          "Hadith.4620 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) who said:\n\"Indeed, Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious, created desire in ten parts, nine parts in men and one part in women.\""
